        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn Mahbub from ‘ Abd Allah ibn Sinan who has narrated the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The shroud is paid for from the whole of the legacy.”’ "
        ]
